#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "ສະບາຍດີ!"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If customers want some additional products, such as laces or innersoles, you"
" can add some to their order in just a few clicks!"
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າລູກຄ້າຕ້ອງການສິນຄ້າເພີ່ມເຕີມ ເຊັ່ນ: ສາຍເກີບ ຫຼື ແຜ່ນຮອງເກີບ, ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນລາຍການສັ່ງຂອງພວ"
"ກເຂົາໄດ້ພຽງແຕ່ບໍ່ກີ່ຄລິກ!"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to your Inventory App, and go to the replenishment from the "
"Operations menu, you can see that some products could be reordered based on "
"those rules."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານໄປທີ່ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ເມນູການເຕີມສິນຄ້າ (replenishment), ທ່ານຈະເຫັນວ່າບາງສິນຄ້"
"າສາມາດສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ໄດ້ຕາມກົດເກນທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້."

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you've added the demo data upon creating this database, it will be "
"populated with demo products, sales orders, purchase orders, and so on. "
"These are nice to go through the various use cases demonstrated below."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກທ່ານໄດ້ເພີ່ມຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງຕອນສ້າງຖານຂໍ້ມູນນີ້, ມັນຈະມີຂໍ້ມູນສິນຄ້າຕົວຢ່າງ, ລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້, ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ ແລະ ອື່ນ"
"ໆ. ເຊິ່ງດີຫຼາຍສຳລັບການທົດລອງໃຊ້ງານຕາມກໍລະນີຕ່າງໆທີ່ສະແດງໄວ້ດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In order to get an overview of all your open tasks, just click the "
"<strong>Project App. </strong>"
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງວຽກທັງໝົດທີ່ກຳລັງດຳເນີນການຢູ່, ພຽງແຕ່ຄລິກ <strong>ແອັບໂຄງການ (Project). "
"</strong>"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Inserting the customer's email address makes it easy for you to send them "
"emails once their order is ready to be picked up again."
msgstr ""
"ການໃສ່ທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມວຂອງລູກຄ້າຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານສົ່ງອີເມວຫາພວກເຂົາໄດ້ງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ ເມື່ອລາຍການສັ່ງຂອງພວກເຂົາພ້ອມໃຫ້ມາ"
"ຮັບແລ້ວ."

