msgid "Leather"
msgstr "ໜັງ"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Marketing Automation</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">,                <strong>Email Marketing</strong>,\n"
"                </font>\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media Marketing</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                , and\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                ."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການທຸກຊ່ອງທາງການສື່ສານຂອງທ່ານໃນບ່ອນດຽວດ້ວຍ Odoo\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດອັດຕະໂນມັດ</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                , <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> <strong>ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວ</"
"strong>,\n"
"                </font>\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານໂຊຊຽວມີເດຍ</"
"font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                , ແລະ\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານ SMS</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                ."

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated environment. (\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting App</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                )"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການວຽກງານບັນຊີຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ງ່າຍກວ່າເກົ່າດ້ວຍລະບົບທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັນຢ່າງສົມບູນ. (\n"
"                <strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ແອັບບັນຊີ</font>\n"
"                </strong>\n"
"                )"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:shoe_maker.product_attribute_value_1
msgid "Men"
msgstr "ຜູ້ຊາຍ"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Next : return to the <strong>Sales App</strong>. You can see that your first order is now ready for pick up, which is indicated by the \"<strong>Ready for Pickup</strong>\" checkbox. At that point, your customer has been notified by\n"
"        email that the order is ready to collect!"
msgstr ""
"ຕໍ່ໄປ: ກັບໄປທີ່ <strong>ແອັບການຂາຍ</strong>. ທ່ານຈະເຫັນວ່າລາຍການສັ່ງທຳອິດຂອງທ່ານພ້ອມໃຫ້ມາຮັບແ"
"ລ້ວ, ເຊິ່ງສະແດງໂດຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍຖືກໃນຊ່ອງ \"<strong>ພ້ອມໃຫ້ມາຮັບ</strong>\". ໃນຂະນະດຽວກັນ, ລູກ"
"ຄ້າຂອງທ່ານກໍໄດ້ຮັບແຈ້ງເຕືອນທາງ\n"
"        ອີເມວແລ້ວວ່າລາຍການສັ່ງພ້ອມໃຫ້ມາຮັບແລ້ວ!"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid "Next up : billing."
msgstr "ຕໍ່ໄປ: ການອອກບິນ."

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Next, go to your Purchase App to open the created purchase order. You can "
"now email your <strong>Request for Quotation</strong> to your vendor or "
"confirm it manually immediately."
msgstr ""
"ຕໍ່ໄປ, ໄປທີ່ແອັບການຈັດຊື້ເພື່ອເປີດໃບສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນ. ທ່ານສາມາດສົ່ງອີເມວ <strong>ໃບຂໍລາຄາ</strong> ຫ"
"າຜູ້ສະໜອງຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ຢືນຢັນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໄດ້ທັນທີ."

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Note that you can easily add services performed which were not initially "
"planned at this stage!"
msgstr ""
"ໝາຍເຫດ: ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມການບໍລິການທີ່ເຮັດເພີ່ມເຕີມ ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ວາງແຜນໄວ້ໃນຕອນທຳອິດໄດ້ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້!"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model:base.automation,name:shoe_maker.null_so_quantity_cancel_related_tasks
msgid "Null SO quantity cancels the related task"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນ SO ເປັນສູນ ຈະຍົກເລີກວຽກທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo ມອບຄວາມເປັນໄປໄດ້ທີ່ບໍ່ຈຳກັດໃຫ້ທ່ານ ເຊັ່ນ:"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model:base.automation,name:shoe_maker.on_last_task_done_turning_order_as_collectible
msgid "On last task done send email: order ready"
msgstr "ເມື່ອວຽກສຸດທ້າຍສຳເລັດ ໃຫ້ສົ່ງອີເມວ: ລາຍການສັ່ງພ້ອມແລ້ວ"

#. module: shoe_maker
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:shoe_maker.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the products are there, you can click the \"<strong>Receipt</strong>\" "
"smart button to validate your receipt and add these new products to your "
"stock."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສິນຄ້າມາຮອດແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"<strong>ໃບຮັບສິນຄ້າ</strong>\" ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນການຮັບ ແລ"
